        or a high-performance model like the <strong>Mercedes-AMG</strong>, our platform ensures a seamless experience for all Mercedes-Benz enthusiasts.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Unmatched Elegance:</strong> Mercedes-Benz is synonymous with luxury, delivering unparalleled comfort and craftsmanship.</li>
        <li><strong>Certified Pre-Owned Assurance:</strong> Find inspected, warrantied vehicles for peace of mind and exceptional quality.</li>
        <li><strong>Diverse Range:</strong> Choose from sporty coupes like the <strong>Mercedes-Benz C-Class</strong> to the flagship
        <strong>Mercedes-Benz S-Class</strong>.</li>
        <li><strong>Effortless Transactions:</strong> Sell your Mercedes-Benz quickly or discover deals through exclusive auctions.</li>
        <li><strong>Innovative Technology:</strong> Explore models featuring Mercedes-Benz’s industry-leading infotainment and safety systems.</li>
      </ul>

    </div>
    <div class="promo-image">
      <%= image_tag "mercedes.png", alt: "Premium Audi cars ready for sale and auction" %>
    </div>
  </div>
